Masewera a '''Olimpiki Ozizira a 202'''2, omwe amatchedwa XXIV Olympic Winter Games, ndi Masewera a 24 a Winter Olympics. Ndi masewera apadziko lonse a nyengo yozizira omwe adzachitika kuyambira pa February 4 mpaka February 20, 2022. Kupikisana kopambana kudalengezedwa m'chilimwe cha 2015 ndipo Beijing idasankhidwa, ndipo popeza idachita nawo Masewera a Olimpiki a Chilimwe a 2008, ukhala mzinda woyamba. kuti achite nawo ma Olympic a Chilimwe ndi Zima.


